  "title": "走る朝",
  "englishTitle": "The Morning Run",
  "category": "curriculum",
  "level": "N4",
  "unlocksAfter": "N4.16",
  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "jp": "冬のある朝、りきぞうは体がとてもつかれていました。毎日、会社の仕事がいそがしくて、家に帰っても元気がありませんでした。仕事もいそがしいですし、運動もしていませんでした し、体がだんだんつかれてきました。冬の朝は寒くて、声も小さくなりました。気分もよくなくて、後でほんとうの病気になりました。",
      "en": "One winter morning, Rikizo's body was very tired. Every day, his work at the company was busy, and even when he got home he had no energy. Work was busy, and he was not exercising at all, and his body gradually grew more tired. The winter mornings were cold, and even his voice became quiet. He did not feel well either, and later he caught a real illness.",
